title: Dragon Ball Super - Spin Battlers (Super Saiyan Vegeta vs. Frieza)
feature: These 2.5" figures may be small in stature, but they're big on battle action.

Place your figure on a spinner stand, harness your finger fury, and knock your opponent’s figure off their spinner before they knock you off yours! You can even combine additional spinners to battle up to three opponents at once.
The Action Two-Pack comes with two figures and two spinner stands – everything you need to get started.
